<div class="title">Close to Death</div>
<div class="substance">Diazepam, Cannabis & & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=DMac&Exact=1">DMac</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; DMac. "Close to Death: An Experience with Diazepam, Cannabis & & Alcohol (exp15491)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 23, 2003. erowid.org/exp/15491</div>

<br/>



